survey_response.review_text: Thanks to Dr. Hormuzd Vakil & Dr. Prasanna Vani. Excellent support staff. Both the doctors explained about my treatment in detail. This gives a sense of satisfaction to the patients. Wishing Dr. Hormuzd & his team  all the very best. God bless.

I have been seeing Dr. Vakil since Jan 2017 when I met with an accident with severe injuries on my face where my lower Jaw was completely crushed and had to undergo a facial trauma. But to my rescue, my case was handled by Vakil, he did a maxillofacial surgery and now my face almost looks like the original even after handling 30 fractures. He was kind, humorous and had incredible ‘bed-side’ manner. Discussing my medical condition with him was like talking to an old friend. The follow-up from his side was really excellent, cannot be explained in words, as he was always available in calls whenever needed. I am still under his care as I am getting treated for dental implants at his clinic, Yatha dental care. He gives you a complete picture of treatment so that we can just sit and relax by completely trusting him with the top class facility and expertise that he has at the clinic. The nightmare of my illness is now slowly becoming a dream of recovery. Credit goes to this wonderful doctor who changed my destiny. I would recommend him to the core.

I know Dr. Vakil from 27th of September 2016. I was admitted in the hospital as a result of an accident that shattered my face and jaws almost completely. I'm really lucky to be under his care. He is a great human being and an absolutely great doctor. I'm back to my regular life thanks to him. Me and my family are thankful to Dr. Vakil, without whom my recovery from that incident wouldn't be possible. I'm still under his care and getting treated for my broken teeth in his clinic. Yatha dental clinic is a top class facility with a lot of equipment for advanced dental treatment. I'm still undergoing treatment and I'm feeling better already.

I had an accident that shattered my face and jaws. Dr. Vakil did my facial reconstruction and Thanks to his care I look like I was before accident. Now I approached Dr. Vakil for my dental treatment for my shattered teeth and he is taking great care of me and the treatment is top class as usual and his clinic has all the advanced equipment. I recommend Dr. Vakil to anyone with absolute confidence.
